      hero.child[Initiative].field[Bonus].value += field[abValue].value]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cSbSSpSens" name="Spellsense" description="Starting at 3rd level, a spellburst savant constantly senses magical auras within 30 feet of her as a supernatural ability, as if they had been concentrating on the {i}detect magic{/i} spell for 1 round. As a move action, she can pinpoint the locations of and identify such auras as if she had concentrated on {i}detect magic{/i} for 3 rounds. At 11th and 19th levels, the range of this ability increases by 30 feet." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Sense magical auras like {i}detect magic{/i}">
