  <thing id="cSbSShiBla" name="Shining Blade" description="{b}Associated Spells:{/b} Spells that require the caster to make an attack roll, spells with a range of personal or touch.\n\n{b}Effect:{/b} The next weapon attack the spellburst savant makes before the start of her next turn deals additional points of damage equal to her Wisdom bonus (if any). This damage can be acid, cold, electricity, fire, or sonic (chosen at the time of casting). If she charged this fundamental with a spell of 2nd level or higher, it deals a further 1d6 points of damage per spell level above 1st.\n\nWhen the spellburst savant activates this fundamental as a standard action, she can also take the attack action while doing so (or, if she wishes, start a full-attack action), applying its effect to the first weapon attack she makes. If she activates it as a swift action while still benefiting from using it as a standard action, the effect applies to the next two attacks she makes (it does not apply twice to one attack)." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Your next weapon attack does more damage" uniqueness="unique">
