  <thing id="cSbSSicSha" name="Sickening Shadows" description="{b}Associated Spells:{/b} Spells that inflict a penalty, area spells that do not deal damage.\n\n{b}Effect:{/b} The spellburst savant wraps herself in dark power, sickening other creatures within 10 feet of her for 1 round (no save). If she charged this fundamental with a spell 2nd level or higher, she can choose to apply the following changes to this effect.\n\n{b}2nd level or higher:{/b} She sickens creatures for 2 rounds.\n\n{b}3rd level or higher:{/b} She sickens creatures within 30 feet.\n\n{b}4th level or higher:{/b} She sickens creatures for 1 minute.\n\n{b}5th level or higher:{/b} She sickens creatures within 60 feet." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You sicken other creatures around you" uniqueness="unique">
