  <thing id="cSbSArmFor" name="Armor of Force" description="The spellburst savant adds her Wisdom bonus (if any) as an armor bonus to her AC. This armor bonus is similar to a {i}mage armor{/i} spell, and protects against incorporeal attacks as well as corporeal ones. It can be suppressed or resumed as a free action." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You add Wisdom as an armor bonus to your AC">
