  <thing id="cSbSWavMot" name="Wave Motion Strike" description="{b}Replaces:{/b} One of the spellburst savant bonus feats.\n\nThe spellburst savant can charge the shining blade fundamental with any spell. If she activates shining blade as both a swift action and a standard action in the same turn, she can apply both effects to the first attack she makes (instead of applying them to one attack each, as she normally would).\n\nFor the purposes of meeting the prerequisites of the Vital Strike feat and any feat that has it as a prerequisite, the spellburst savant&apos;s base attack bonus from her spellburst savant class levels is equal to her spellburst savant level. She can take such feats as spellburst savant bonus feats, if she wishes.\n\n{b}Note: This ability&apos;s effect isn&apos;t implemented.{/b}" compset="CustomSpec" summary="You have a more powerful shining blade" uniqueness="unique">
