  <thing id="cSbSPatExp" name="The Path of Explosions" description="{b}Replaces:{/b} One of the spellburst savant bonus feats.\n\nThe spellburst savant can charge the nova flare fundamental with any spell. Once per round, when she activates nova flare, she can deal an additional 1d8 points of damage, plus a further 1d8 points of damage per five spellburst savant caster levels. In addition, whenever the spellburst savant activates nova flare, she can center the effect on any grid intersection within 10 feet + 10 feet per level of the spell she charged the fundamental with. It affects all creatures and objects within 10 feet of that point other than the spellburst savant and her equipment." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You have a more powerful nova flare fundamental" uniqueness="unique">
