  <thing id="cSbSInsSha" name="Insidious Shadows" description="{b}Replaces:{/b} One of the spellburst savant bonus feats.\n\nThe spellburst savant can charge the sickening shadows fundamental with any spell. Once per round, when she activates sickening shadows, she can imbue it into herself or an ally she touches instead of using it normally. The first time within the next 1 minute per spellburst savant caster level the imbued ally hits a creature with a melee attack, the fundamental activates, centered on the creature struck. Neither you nor the imbued ally are affected by it, but every other creature in the area is." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You have a more powerful sickening shadows fundamental" uniqueness="unique">
