  <thing id="cSbSBulSto" name="Bullet Storm" description="{b}Replaces:{/b} One of the spellburst savant bonus feats.\n\nThe spellburst savant can charge the starspray fundamental with any spell. Once per round, when she activates starspray, she can make and hurl one additional mote of elemental matter. If she hits a target with a mote, any further starspray attacks she aims at that target until the end of her next turn automatically without having to roll (they are still considered individual attacks)." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You have a more powerful starspray fundamental" uniqueness="unique">
