  <thing id="cSbSArBFam" name="Arcane Bond (Familiar)" description="A familiar is a magical pet that enhances the spellburst savant&apos;s skills and senses and can aid her in magic. Rules for familiars appear in Chapter 3 of the {i}Pathfinder Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook{/i}." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Gain a familiar">
