  <thing id="arSbSMagMa" name="Magpie Mage" description="{i}&quot;The best magic is built on stolen ideas and borrowed spellbooks!&quot;\n—Mary Kirin, a magpie mage{/i}\n\nWhen a spellburst savant first encounters magic for the first time in their lives, they tend to go into a frenzy, feeling a powerful need to learn more of this new power they didn&apos;t know they had. For some, this feeling never leaves. As a result of their hoarding of magical experiences, magpie mages are copycat extraordinaires, building spells on the fly even after only seeing them once." compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
