  <thing id="arSbSMedit" name="Spellburst Meditant" description="{i}&quot;This hand of mine glows with an awesome power! Its burning grip tells me to defeat you!&quot;\n—Kasu D&apos;om, a spellburst meditant{/i}\n\nMost spellburst savants take on the role of battlefield artillery, and those who bring their talents to melee combat tend to bring weaponry to bear, channeling power along their blades to kill their foes. The warriors known as spellburst meditants eschew that path, honing their bodies as well as their minds to transform themselves into deadly weapons in their own right." compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
